headline: Jack Henry's transaction enrichment, powered by Bud Financial, brings greater clarity and accuracy to digital banking experiences
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) today announced the successful rollout of its native transaction enrichment capabilities on the Banno Digital Platform™, delivered in collaboration with Bud Financial ("Bud").
